<div class="action-box">
<div class="inner">
<ul class="entry-management-links icon-links"><li class="link mem_add first-item"><a href="https://www.dreamwidth.org/tools/memadd?journal=transitional_writes&amp;itemid=39813" ><img border='0' width="16" height="16" alt="Add Memory" title="Add Memory" src="https://www.dreamwidth.org/img/silk/entry/memories_add.png"  /></a></li>
<li class="link tell_friend"><a href="https://www.dreamwidth.org/tools/tellafriend?journal=transitional_writes&amp;itemid=39813" ><img border='0' width="16" height="16" alt="Share This Entry" title="Share This Entry" src="https://www.dreamwidth.org/img/silk/entry/tellafriend.png"  /></a></li>
</ul></div>
